openMinded_db_lib

THIS LIBRARY IS A PROPERTY OF SHAGGYDOGS

It provides simple and easy to use funtions that make the link betwin a C program and a PostgreSQL database.
This is the first version of the library and due to that, the database options are not configurable for the moment.

Due to that, the database should respect the following specifications :
Name: zuser
User: zuser
Password: zinsa2010
Server: localhost

Tables : 
Flight(integer flight_id)
Classes(integer class_id, text class_name)
BasicSensors(integer data_id, integer time, float altitude, float pitch, float roll, float vyaw, float vx, float vy, float vz, float ax, float ay, float az, integer classe)
You will find enclosed to this library the sql scripts that generated these tables.
